Perl6::Pod
=====================

Perl6::Pod - use Perl6's pod in perl5 programms


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 Regexp::Grammars

SEE ALSO

JavaScript implementation of pod6
  
I highly recommend see pod6 implementation <https://github.com/zag/js-
pod6>. That is modern implementation of pod6. Also check project site
<https://pod6.in> for latest information about pod6.

